      </p>

      <h2>2. Terms of Use</h2>
      <p>
        Users may use this app for personal, non-commercial purposes only.
        Users must not enter or misuse another person's information without their consent.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Paid Services</h2>
      <p>
        Some features (compatibility, monthly horoscopes) are available through in-app purchases.
        Payments are processed in accordance with Apple App Store policies, and refunds follow Apple's refund policy.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        The Saju analysis and fortune results provided by this service are entertainment content based on traditional East Asian philosophy.
        They should not be used as a basis for important life decisions.
