      <p>
        The operator may modify these terms as needed. Any changes will be posted on this page.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For inquiries regarding these terms: <a href="mailto:ccaja21@naver.com">ccaja21@naver.com</a>
      </p>
      </article>
    </main>
    <Footer lang="en" />
  </body>
</html>
